Title: Relates to requiring a sentence of imprisonment for sex offenses where the victim of the offense lacked the ability to consent due to incapacity
Summary: Relates to requiring a sentence of imprisonment for sex offenses where the victim of the offense lacked the ability to consent due to incapacity.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the penal law, in relation to requiring a sentence of imprisonment for sex offenses where the victim of the offense lacked the ability to consent due to incapacity
